### Profile Sync - Save profile (replace @token with a valid JWT)
POST http://localhost:8080/profile-sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "theme": "dark",
    "notifications": true,
    "language": "pt-BR",
    "auto_connect": false,
    "selected_server": "us-east-1"
  }
}

### Profile Sync - Update profile
POST http://localhost:8080/profile-sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "theme": "light",
    "notifications": true,
    "language": "en-US",
    "auto_connect": true
  }
}

### Profile Sync - No auth header
POST http://localhost:8080/profile-sync
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {
    "theme": "dark"
  }
}

### Profile Sync - Empty profile
POST http://localhost:8080/profile-sync
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "profile": {}
}
